[{"id":798641,"node":"职场话题","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1629906755","description":"<p>因为经常看到 offer 对比，大部分声音都是劝选择公务员，但是不太理解体制内的好处</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/798641","replies":164,"created_ts":1630218992,"created":"14:36:32","title":"想问一下大家觉得体制内工作好在那里","author":"cool4food","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/cool4food","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0af5/3370/500180_mini.png?m=1595659109"},{"id":798620,"node":"macOS","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/macos","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_mini.png?m=1607656854","description":"我在站内搜了一下. 好久没有讨论这个问题了- -<br /><br />不理解的是. 大家都说 macos 对开发友好, 但是复制粘贴这些快捷键大家是通过修改配置 / 键盘映射? 还是习惯默认快捷键?<br /><br />用左手小手指按 cmd 还是用大拇指?<br /><br />很方便吗?<br /><br />另外本人现在用 windows + docker 开发也不错啊.<br /><br />主要是看到一些招聘贴说入职标配 macbook pro 担心去了那样的公司不适应 mac.","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/798620","replies":105,"created_ts":1630211243,"created":"12:27:23","title":"macos 对开发友好在哪里?","author":"chaleaoch","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/chaleaoch","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/92e0/46b3/126993_mini.png?m=1622082563"},{"id":798636,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1629391393","description":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/798636","replies":101,"created_ts":1630218104,"created":"14:21:44","title":"头条、网易新闻什么的变味了，大家现在用什么 app 看新闻？国内/外的 app 都行","author":"goodhellonice","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/goodhellonice","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a66b/6c3e/487715_mini.png?m=1615460716"},{"id":798675,"node":"宽带症候群","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1620107025","description":"<p>除了电信(电信价位不敢想)，移动和联通哪家宽带稍微好点，1000 兆宽带，移动宽带比联通稍微便宜点，同时还送智能安防，送千兆路由器，送 IPTV......</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/798675","replies":71,"created_ts":1630229397,"created":"17:29:57","title":"选宽带上面的一些困扰","author":"nanjingwuyanzu","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/nanjingwuyanzu","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a8cf5af415d43f70ef20c795f3a0f0ef?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":798669,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1629391393","description":"<p>刚刚看到了考公的帖子，就想请教下大家，考公和入职哪个比较好？</p>\n<br/>\n<p>目前状态：毕业</p>\n<p>考公：月薪 5k，稳定，福利待遇好（具体怎么好我不知道），但是就算福利再好年薪也不能过 30 吧。</p>\n<p>入职：月薪 15k，955，大概年薪税前可以接近 30 ？</p>\n<br/>\n<p>考公只有这一次，之后不能再考。</p>\n<br/>\n<p>主要考虑问题是买房，以上两个选择的工作地点都是国内某一线城市，考公感觉买房有点困难，不想靠父母。</p>\n<p>父母强烈推荐考公，可能毕竟稳定，而且也说出去好听一点？</p>\n<br/>\n想请教下各位的意见。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/798669","replies":53,"created_ts":1630227229,"created":"16:53:49","title":"考公 or 入职？","author":"Zhancha","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Zhancha","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/50e6/b547/434804_mini.png?m=1565341086"},{"id":798586,"node":"宽带症候群","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1620107025","description":"<p>4G/5G 信号频率高，穿透差，想运营商往跟前修基站还会被反智人士阻扰，这个时候自己动手丰衣足食就很重要了，少像巨婴一样只会哇哇叫投诉，自己花点小钱省心省时，还不用跟运营商的持久推诿扯皮</p>\n<p>本体\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/wQZNMYj.png\" rel=\"nofollow\">i.imgur.com/wQZNMYj.png</a></p>\n<p>室外天线（隔离一定要做好）\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/fyxdXEa.png\" rel=\"nofollow\">i.imgur.com/fyxdXEa.png</a></p>\n<p>4G 信号直接满格，测速十几 M\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/NMNczeP.png\" rel=\"nofollow\">i.imgur.com/NMNczeP.png</a></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/798586","replies":44,"created_ts":1630173055,"created":"01:50:55","title":"联通信号差，自己动手解决","author":"feast","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/feast","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/677e/7b5a/252428_mini.png?m=1511185899"},{"id":798635,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1629391416","description":"<p>之前发现 fish bash 交互做的挺不错的然后打算用段时间,装完了后 chsh 改默认 shell,结果另一个员工把 fish 给卸了导致 root 用户无法进行 SSH 远程登录，后来经过一晚上的折腾进入 centOS 的安全模式后新增用户并赋予管理员权限才缓解过来...，有惊无险的一个 8 月 13 日晚上,主要是当时主机上有 Jira Software 而且开发商务什么的都还在用着</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/798635","replies":41,"created_ts":1630217310,"created":"14:08:30","title":"关于 fish shell 的一个误操作坑","author":"KomiSans","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/KomiSans","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0fd1/63b6/442540_mini.png?m=1619937258"},{"id":798677,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1615111825","description":"<p>如题，se 和 12 mini 也就 150g 内，为什么不用剩下的 50 多 g 来加大电池容量呢？</p>\n<p>堆到 200g 厚一点，换一个 4000mAh 的大电池也好哇。</p>\n<p>反正现在人均用 200 多 g 的习武之人，牺牲一点轻薄换超强续航也是不错的选择呀😂</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/798677","replies":40,"created_ts":1630230604,"created":"17:50:04","title":"为什么苹果不出一款小屏幕的全面屏 se，用大电池","author":"zhengfan2016","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/zhengfan2016","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/df526f138d10cac8c95b274c720a6f55?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":798679,"node":"分享创造","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/create","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1629391403","description":"<p>她刚刚高考完，有一天问我会不会写浏览器插件。我刚好刚写了一个浏览器插件，还没写完，虽然还不是很了解浏览器插件的开发。但是她让我帮帮她，于是我就帮帮她了。最后我们两个人折腾好一会完成了这个插件。</p>\n<p>大家如果有用这个功能的，可以参与到开源中，添加你需要的搜索引擎 💖</p>\n<h2>相关链接</h2>\n<p>GitHub： <a href=\"https://github.com/lcandy2/oSearch/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/lcandy2/oSearch/</a></p>\n<p>Chrome： <a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/pejlgjjlbhpbfiiaegahmeahlhbpkglo\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/pejlgjjlbhpbfiiaegahmeahlhbpkglo</a></p>\n<p>Firefox： <a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/firefox/addon/osearch\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://addons.mozilla.org/firefox/addon/osearch</a></p>\n<h2>功能</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>为列表中的网站添加 OpenSearch，来让浏览器将其添加到搜索引擎</li>\n<li>搜索引擎添加完成后，在地址栏中输入网站地址，按下 空格键 或 Tab 即可快速搜索</li>\n<li>在 Firefox 浏览器中，需要手动点击带有加号的网站图标将其添加至搜索引擎中。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>截图</h2>\n<p><img alt=\"oSearch helps you search wikipedia.org via OpenSearch\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/akylvy.png\"/>\n<img alt=\"oSearch helps in adding search engines\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/pzn8ns.png\"/></p>\n<h2>更多内容</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/lcandy2/oSearch/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/lcandy2/oSearch/</a></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/798679","replies":31,"created_ts":1630231881,"created":"18:11:21","title":"和一个小妹妹一起写了一个浏览器插件","author":"nexmoe","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/nexmoe","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c7fd185f8c967dec20c29c75a40b9e09?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":798656,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1629391393","description":"经常国外购物，有些平台只支持信用卡，但是很多国外的虚拟信用卡平台要么不支持国内的卡，要么流程很繁琐，而且收费也不便宜。我知道国内很多银行都有提供虚拟信用卡服务，我问了下招行是只有银联的。有没有人用这种服务可以推荐一下吗? 谢谢!","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/798656","replies":24,"created_ts":1630223109,"created":"15:45:09","title":"请问哪家银行提供非银联的虚拟信用卡?","author":"vincentxue","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/vincentxue","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8ed6/f784/77351_mini.png?m=1463112915"},{"id":798688,"node":"Windows","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1583044904","description":"<p>需要把电脑重装下，请问有什么推荐的迁移工具吗</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/798688","replies":21,"created_ts":1630234250,"created":"18:50:50","title":"求推荐 Windows 下重装系统迁移工具","author":"huyinjie","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/huyinjie","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1856/2c44/71429_mini.png?m=1576686677"},{"id":798588,"node":"职场话题","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","node_image":